它的作用是代替流產手術，藉助吸力來清除掉子宮裡的殘留物。但是這一手術用的並不是簡單的機器，而是專業的醫療設備。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://p3.pstatp.com/large/pgc-image/a7d9de3667fc4099a6baa54b6a6b4d23\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fp3.pstatp.com%2Flarge%2Fpgc-image%2Fa7d9de3667fc4099a6baa54b6a6b4d23&h=9132d240&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n這兩位女孩用吸取器來抽吸經血以縮短經期時間的行為是沒有任何根據的。醫生也警告所有女性千萬別這麼做，否則可能會造成陰道損傷感染，嚴重的話會造成生殖器和子宮頸受損，導致失血休克。經血的流速之所以穩定，就是要讓人體能夠承受，但吸取器可能造成相差1000倍的大出血，身體無法承受，就會導致大出血休克。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T14:15:27.000Z","msg":"個兩條女係咪等唔切玩Gangbang<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14771434a23c5f0e5e95e3de299bb60a5d950d58","tid":1882883,"uid":82389,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T14:15:30.000Z","msg":"鬼妹為左可以玩真係弱撚智<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"500448fe0ba129bf989da34864715f28a0a72d26","tid":1882883,"uid":29523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T14:16:00.000Z","msg":"西洋版究極花與蛇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"579e7a148cf4b572462b991eee956e9cf0e87088","tid":1882883,"uid":61831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T14:16:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7834664213d8cba320b06a36db6b1ca0cf448d3","tid":1882883,"uid":53672,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T14:16:26.000Z","msg":"吸塵機吸兩吸 成個子宮扯出黎都得"},{"pid":"bd7bb1268b4cf5cc601d4065aeb76bc522ff0851","tid":1882883,"uid":153781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T14:16:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f02f12db09d9cb33eda987f2c183f3d651f770fe","tid":1882883,"uid":9104,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyT